(
  'SAMPLE-COSTABLANCA',
  'Costa Blanca South off-plan apartments under €250k with 3+ bedrooms within 1km of the beach',
  encode(sha256('sample-costablanca'::bytea), 'hex'),
  '{"region":"cb-south","type":"Apartment","max_price":250000,"min_beds":3,"max_beach_km":1.0,"status":"off-plan"}'::jsonb,
  array['SAMPLE-6', 'SAMPLE-7', 'SAMPLE-8']::text[],
  '{
    "sections": [
      {"title": "Investment Thesis", "body": "Costa Blanca South off-plan apartments in the sub-€250k band represent the highest-velocity segment in Spanish coastal property. The cohort is dominated by 3-bedroom new-builds in Torrevieja, Orihuela Costa, Villamartín, and Pilar de la Horadada — all within 1km of the beach, all targeting the UK retail-buyer + Norwegian/Swedish second-home pipeline. Avena''s hedonic OLS places fair-market reference at €2,400-2,800/m² for this profile; the top-quartile of the universe trades at €2,150-2,350/m², a 7-12% discount to reference.\n\nOff-plan status delivers two structural edges: (a) staged-payment financing limits upfront capital exposure to 20-30%, and (b) handover values rise 8-12% from contract signing to key-ready as the cohort moves up Avena''s status curve. Yield support comes from short-let demand on the costa coast — gross yields of 5.5-6.4% are typical with 60-65% occupancy."},
      {"title": "Universe & Selection", "body": "Filter applied: region=cb-south, type=Apartment, max price €250k, min 3 bedrooms, max beach distance 1km, status=off-plan. Universe of 23 properties; ranked by composite (Avena Score + underprice). Top 3 selected. All carry communal pools, key-ready dates between 2027-Q1 and 2027-Q4, and developer Counterpart scores ≥65."},
      {"title": "Valuation Analysis", "body": "Universe median asking €/m²: €2,290. Hedonic OLS reference: €2,580. Underprice gap: 11.2% — wide for a residential segment, narrow for the off-plan cohort where staged-payment discount is conventional. Top pick prices at €2,185/m² (€225k ask, 103m² built, 3-bed Orihuela Costa). Median underprice across the top 3: 9.8%."},
      {"title": "Yield Projection", "body": "Bottom-up ADR model on AirDNA Torrevieja + Orihuela Costa sample (n=518, 2024-2026). Projected gross yield range 5.5-6.4%. Net yield (after platform 15%, management 18%, reserve 5%, taxes): 3.7-4.6%. Cash-on-cash with 70% mortgage LTV at Euribor 3M + 1.65bps: 9.4-12.1%. Occupancy modelled at 61% (Torrevieja) to 68% (Orihuela Costa frontline)."},
      {"title": "Counterpart Risk", "body": "Three developers in the candidate set: TM GRUPO INMOBILIARIO (AV, score 74), AEDAS HOMES (AV, score 72), and HERZOG PROMOTIONS (ABV, score 68). All three have post-2008 track records and active project pipelines elsewhere on Costa Blanca. No active court judgements; payment-delay signals at acceptable levels. Banking exposure spread across Sabadell, Bankinter, and Caja Rural — modest concentration risk."},
      {"title": "Macro Context", "body": "Same supportive macro as broader Spain thesis: ECB easing, Euribor falling, foreign-buyer share rising, mortgage approvals +8.3% YoY. Costa Blanca specifically: Alicante notarial transactions +7.1% YoY (stable). Foreign-buyer composition in Torrevieja: UK 31%, Norway 12%, Sweden 9%, Belgium 7%, Germany 5% — well-diversified, no single-nationality dependency."},
      {"title": "Scenario Stress Test", "body": "Genesis 24-month horizon (post-handover):\n\n  BULL (P25): +14.2% capital appreciation post-handover. Driver: cohort moves up the off-plan-to-ready status premium.\n  BASE (P50): +9.4%. Drivers: trend continuation, modest underprice narrowing.\n  BEAR (P75): -2.8%. Drivers: handover delays > 6 months (probability 14%), regional supply spike, or specific developer financial stress.\n\nOff-plan-specific risk: developer non-completion. Mitigated by aval bancario (Spain mandatory bank guarantee on staged payments — capital is preserved even on developer failure)."},
      {"title": "Comparable Transactions", "body": "Notarial sample, 12-month rolling, Costa Blanca South 3-bed apartments €180-260k (n=219). Median sale-to-list 0.952 (4.8% effective discount). DOM median 64 days for ready stock, 28 days for off-plan. Off-plan stock turning over faster — confirmed structural shortage. Mean handover-to-list price uplift: +9.1% over a 14-month median construction window."},
      {"title": "Position Sizing", "body": "From a hypothetical €1M deployment book (staged 20-30% per property at contract):\n\n  Property #1 — 40% of book commitment (€90k staged payment at contract on €225k ask)\n  Property #2 — 35% (€80k staged on €230k ask)\n  Property #3 — 25% (€60k staged on €245k ask)\n\nTotal upfront capital deployed: €230k against €700k total commitment. Balance staged at construction milestones over 14 months. Reserve €100k for opportunistic ready-stock buying at 5%+ discount to model."},
      {"title": "Exit Strategy", "body": "Post-handover hold 24 months (total cycle 38 months from contract). Exit triggers:\n\n  1. Handover +9 months MTM gain > 12% → list 1 unit, hold 2\n  2. Bubble Scanner Torrevieja > 75 → full exit\n  3. Yield compression below 4.5% net → exit lowest-yielding\n  4. Regional supply +20% YoY → halt add-on, accelerate exit timeline\n\nLiquidity assessment: high — 3-bed Costa Blanca apartments under €250k turn over in 70 DOM median. Exit channel: a mix of Engel & Völkers, Kyero, and regional agencies."}
    ],
    "candidates": [
      {"ref":"AV-CB-201","name":"3-Bed Frontline Apartment, Orihuela Costa","location":"Orihuela Costa, Alicante","type":"Apartment","price_eur":225000,"pm2":2185,"mm2":2480,"built_m2":103,"bedrooms":3,"beach_km":0.4,"score":74,"yield_gross":6.2,"url":"#","image":null,"underprice_pct":11.9,"yield_net_estimate":4.3,"developer":"TM GRUPO INMOBILIARIO","developer_grade":"AV","developer_score":74,"energy":"A","completion":"2027-Q1","one_liner":"Strongest pick: 11.9% under reference, AV developer, A-rated energy.","risk_note":"Handover scheduled Q1 2027 — 8-month construction risk window."},
      {"ref":"AV-CB-202","name":"3-Bed Penthouse, Torrevieja","location":"Torrevieja, Alicante","type":"Apartment","price_eur":230000,"pm2":2250,"mm2":2520,"built_m2":102,"bedrooms":3,"beach_km":0.6,"score":71,"yield_gross":5.9,"url":"#","image":null,"underprice_pct":10.7,"yield_net_estimate":4.1,"developer":"AEDAS HOMES","developer_grade":"AV","developer_score":72,"energy":"A","completion":"2027-Q2","one_liner":"Penthouse with solarium — premium configuration at near-median pricing.","risk_note":"Solarium adds 12-18m² usable but not in built area — yield model adjusted conservatively."},
      {"ref":"AV-CB-203","name":"3-Bed Apartment, Villamartín","location":"Villamartín, Alicante","type":"Apartment","price_eur":245000,"pm2":2335,"mm2":2550,"built_m2":105,"bedrooms":3,"beach_km":0.9,"score":68,"yield_gross":5.5,"url":"#","image":null,"underprice_pct":8.4,"yield_net_estimate":3.8,"developer":"HERZOG PROMOTIONS","developer_grade":"ABV","developer_score":68,"energy":"B","completion":"2027-Q4","one_liner":"Golf-resort adjacent — yield model accounts for off-season constraint.","risk_note":"Construction completion 2027-Q4 — longest hold-to-handover in the universe."}
    ]
  }'::jsonb,
  'Costa Blanca South off-plan 3-bed apartments at €2,185-2,335/m² trade 8-12% below hedonic reference, supported by mandatory aval bancario protection on staged payments. Top 3 picks deliver projected 9.4% capital appreciation through handover + 4.0% net yield post-key. Recommendation: BUY at €1M total commitment, staged payments capped at €230k upfront. 38-month full cycle.',
  'BUY',
  78,
  'curated-sample-v1',
